data.name: WhatWeDoinTextLbl.Text
data.value: We are developing a program for the game Vietcong 1, which is quite old, dating back to 2003. We are creating an application called VcComHub that allows players to connect to a game server with any game mode from a single place. Our goal is to connect players and clans, bringing the community together to revive this game and ensure it doesn't fade into obscurity. By centralizing server access and fostering a vibrant player base, we aim to breathe new life into Vietcong 1 and keep its legacy alive.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: VcComHub is a product of collaboration and dedication by a team of passionate individuals who have put their hearts into making this project a success. We are Delta Devs, a group of developers, testers, and translators united by our love for gaming and technology.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
One-Click Addon Integration: Join your favorite Vietcong servers effortlessly with all required addons in place. No more juggling multiple files or configurations.
In-Game Chat Integration: Stay connected with other players even if you're not in the game. VcComHub enables you to chat with your friends and teammates while they are on the server, ensuring you never miss out on important communications.
Developer Tools: We understand the importance of a smooth development process. Our application includes a section specifically for developers to simplify and streamline their work on Vietcong-related projects. Although this feature is currently in beta, we are continuously improving it based on user feedback.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Welcome to VcComHub, an innovative application designed specifically for Vietcong enthusiasts. VcComHub revolutionizes the way players connect to servers by allowing them to join with all necessary addons through a single icon. This streamlined process eliminates the hassle of managing multiple addons and enhances the overall gaming experience.
